rounds.response:
Let’s evaluate the deal from my perspective.

Current value (what I would give away)  
• 5 Wheat → 5 × 6 = 30  
• 3 Sheep → 3 × 12 = 36  
• 1 Ore   → 1 × 33 = 33  
Total value leaving my hand: 30 + 36 + 33 = 99

Value of incoming goods  
• 5 Brick → 5 × 27 = 135  
• 2 Wood  → 2 × 12 = 24  
Total value entering my hand: 135 + 24 = 159

Net change: +60 value—great for me. Because the offer is already extremely favorable, and I don’t want to risk losing it, I accept immediately.

[Accept]
